Counter-Strike: Source

TITLE: CSS:GG map - GG Cargoyard map
AUTHOR: Sota Poika
E-MAIL: omg91@hotmail.com.com
WEBSITE: -

FILENAME: gg_cargoyard.bsp
FILESIZE: 4.102 mb
DATE RELEASED: 18 april 2008

CREDITS: TempletonPack for his patience to wait for this map to be fixed.

INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS: Extract cstrike -folder to X:\Program Files\Valve\Steam\SteamApps\\counter-strike source (Where the "X" is your drive)

DESCRIPTION: This is my attempt to remake CoD4 map mp_shipment for Counter-Strike: Source. I tried to make this as the greatest mp_shipment remake for now.

This map was made in 2 days, kinda "speed mapping" for me. Also, this is my first GunGame map, hope this goes to some servers with GunGame maps. Mail me the server IP if you use this map in your server.

BUGS: Weird light casting in containers caused by optimizing techniques I used.
